description: Lincoln Tree Farm is an eclectic mix of open areas and forests of varying visibility and thickness, with a fairly extensive trail network crisscrossing throughout. Contour detail is generally quite subtle, mapped contours are 2m as opposed to the usual 5m. Courses by Will Enger.
Ft. Steilacoom Park has a variety of orienteering experiences including open parkland, steep forested trails, and an urban/campus secion. Courses by Jourdan Harvey.
